pair.value: This process is called after a contract modification request is raised. This flow will allow the contracts group to view the request details and send for information gathering.

One sub process for each person added in the start form to collect information. Controlled in "Other" tab to determine when to move forward.
Used internally to get the following information (Request for Information/Structure); - Financial cost and assessment - List of approvals needed to negotiate -Key information about the range that functional leads are allowed to negotiate - Approval amounts - Contract deadline - Task escalation
